Expense Tracker:
Allows users to input expenses (name and amount).
Displays a list of added expenses.
Keeps the expense records on the same page dynamically.

Investment Tips:
Provides tips and advice on making smart investment decisions.
Helps users understand how to make their money work for them.
Smart Saving Plans:

Suggests strategies for saving money and building a secure financial future.
Tips include automation, setting goals, and using apps for better financial management.

User-Friendly UI/UX:
Simple, clean, and easy-to-use interface for managing expenses.
Mobile-responsive design.
